                        <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart me-3"></i>S·∫£n Ph·∫©m Cinema City
                    </h1>
                    <p class="products-hero-subtitle">Kh√°m ph√° c√°c s·∫£n ph·∫©m ti·ªán √≠ch v√† ƒë·ªì ƒÉn th·ª©c u·ªëng tuy·ªát v·ªùi t·∫°i r·∫°p</p>
                </div>
