                    <!-- D·ªØ li·ªáu s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c t·∫£i t·ª´ API v√† hi·ªÉn th·ªã ·ªü ƒë√¢y -->
                </div>


                <nav aria-label="Ph√¢n trang s·∫£n ph·∫©m">
                    <ul class="pagination">
